overview: Brayden's your quintessential boy next door — adorable and sexy, athletic and charming, charismatic and outgoing — with a wild sex-loving side Corbin Fisher fans can't get enough of. In CF Crush: Brayden Vol. 2, we join the endlessly endearing and supremely sexy young stud as he first explores sex with a man, then embraces and unleashes his insatiable lust with Harper, Tom, Kennedy, Jacob, and Kellan!
title: CF Crush: Brayden 2
